quran[23]{c,v,t,f}:
  88,25,"Chisimu Kukwetu pe ni kwakuujila kwao."
  88,26,"Soni chisimu kuŵalanjidwa kwao kuli Nowe."
  89,22,"Ni kwika Ambuje ŵenu (Allah kukwiilanya magambo), Achimalaika ali ndandanda!"
  89,23,"Ni kwikanajo lyele lisikulyo Jahannama! Lyele lisikulyo mundu tachikumbuchila (yaŵapanganyisye), nambo ana kuchinkamuchisya chichi kwele kumbuchilako?"
  89,24,"Tachiti (pakuligamba): “Nkongwene! Bola ngalongosye (yambone yakungamuchisya) pa umi wangu (walelo uno).”"
  90,16,"Kapena masikini jwaluwunduwundupe (ligongo lyakulaga nnope)."
  90,17,"Soni nikuŵa (nkutola yakulyajo) jumpepe mwa aŵala ŵaakulupilile, ni kulimbikasyanaga ya kupilila soni ni kulimbikasyanaga ya kutendelana chanasa."
  90,18,"Ŵanganyao niŵandu ŵakun'dyo (ŵali ŵambone)."
  91,13,"Basi Ntenga jwa Allah (Swaleh) ŵasalile kuti: “(Aji ni) ngamiya ja Allah, sano ngasin'jikanyaga kumwa mesi (palisiku lyakwe)."
  91,14,"Nambo ŵankaaniile nikujiulaga; basi Ambuje ŵao ŵajonasile ligongo lya chileŵi chao; niŵalandenye pachonasikocho."
  91,15,"Soni jwangajogopa yakuichisya yakwe."
  92,10,"Basi chitun'jepepachisye litala lyausito (lyakutendela yakusakala)."
  92,11,"Soni ngasichija kunkamuchisya chipanje chakwe ndema jagwila (ku Moto)."
  92,12,"Chisimu Kukwetu nikwachili chongolo."
  93,7,"Soni ni ŵansimene n'di ŵangachimanya chongoko (jajili Qur'an ni malamusi ga Dini) nikun'jongola?"
  93,8,"Ni ŵansimene soni n'di ŵakulaga nikunsichilisya?"
  93,9,"Sano mwanache jwawina basi ngasimunchima."
  94,4,"Ni tunnyakuliile kusaalidwa kwenu?"
  94,5,"Basi chisimu pakuli kunonopa pana kwepepala."
  94,6,"Chisimu pakuli kunonopa pana kwepepala."
  95,1,"Nguulumbila nkuju ni nzaituni."
  95,2,"Ni litumbi lya Sinai."
  95,3,"Kwisa soni awu nsinda (wa Maaka) wantunjelele."